description:
(Part 3 of 3) When most people think of the book of Revelation they think of mysterious beasts, a frightful dragon, doom, gloom, and Armageddon. But scattered throughout its pages are seven rich blessings that can positively change your life. Steve Wohlberg and Joel Haywood explain the seven blessings which will help prepare you to live forever in the New Jerusalem where God's love reigns supreme.
